  "text": "where log(yield ) i,t-1 is log yield instrumented with (July Temp)t-1 and (July Temp)t-2. [CITATION_1] To understand the specification, note first that current-i.e., year t-temperature obviously has a [CITATION_2] As usual, \u03b7 t and \u03bb i are year and county fixed effects.",
